  "description": "The most transparent demonstration of the 5-limit attractor: maximum field strength (0.9), very slow attack (0.5s), held in reverb. Every note you play gradually bends toward its 5-limit just ratio. Sustain long enough and you hear equal temperament dissolve into pure mathematics. The pad itself disappears — only the tuning system remains.",
